sub_title: Founder & CEO - Shypple - Manage your logistics remotely
summary:
We are a full-service digital freight forwarder, empowered by intuitive, plug & play software. Through digitised supply chain dashboards we bring end-to-end visibility to modern logistics teams.

Experienced Founder with a demonstrated history of working in the logistics and supply chain industry. Skilled Entrepreneurship, Software Product Design, Finance and Accounting.
